        <Parent_String>cracks [300209168], conditions and effects by specific type [300389722], Conditions and Effects (hierarchy name) [300186269], Physical Attributes Facet [300264087]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
